        { q: "What is Blue Sky Maine?", a: "Blue Sky Maine is a vertically integrated cannabis company based in Farmington. They cultivate, extract, and retail cannabis through two storefronts. Their product line includes MOFGA-certified organic flower, live resin, shatter, batter, diamonds, and cartridges." },
